---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad"
  description="Learn about Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College's history, vision, mission, values, and leadership — a trusted co-educational school in Vijay Nagar, Ghaziabad since 1999."
  pubDate={new Date("August 08 2021")}
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> / <span>About Us</span>
      </div>
      <h1>About Saraswati Shiksha Niketan</h1>
      <p>
        Twenty-six years of shaping confident, capable learners in the heart of
        Vijay Nagar, Ghaziabad.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">School Overview</span>
        <h2>A Legacy of Learning in Ghaziabad</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College is a co-educational
          institution located at Krishna Nagar Bagu, Vijay Nagar, Ghaziabad,
          offering education from Nursery through Intermediate (Class 12) under
          the Uttar Pradesh Board.
        </p>
        <p>
          What began as a modest neighbourhood school in 1999 has grown into one
          of Vijay Nagar's most trusted institutions, known for disciplined
          academics, dedicated faculty, and a genuine focus on every child's
          development — not just their marksheet.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-2 mt-lg">
          <div>
            <div
              class="stat-num"
              style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"
            >
              2,400+
            </div><div
              class="stat-label"
              style="color:var(--color-text-soft);font-size:0.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;"
            >
              Students
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div
              class="stat-num"
              style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);"
            >
              85+
            </div><div
              class="stat-label"
              style="color:var(--color-text-soft);font-size:0.85rem;text-transform:uppercase;"
            >
              Faculty Members
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;">
        <div class="seal" style="--seal-size:220px;">
          <div class="seal-inner">
            <span class="est-label">Established</span>
            <span class="est-year">1999</span>
            <span class="est-sub">UP Board Affiliated</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Journey</span>
        <h2>School History</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <span class="year">1999</span><h4>Foundation</h4><p>
            Saraswati Shiksha Niketan opens its doors in Vijay Nagar with
            Nursery to Class 5, and 120 founding students.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <span class="year">2006</span><h4>Secondary Section Introduced</h4><p>
            The school expands to High School level, adding science and commerce
            laboratories to the campus.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <span class="year">2012</span><h4>Intermediate College Status</h4><p>
            Recognised by the Uttar Pradesh Board to offer Classes 11 and 12
            across Science, Commerce, and Humanities.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <span class="year">2018</span><h4>Smart Campus Upgrade</h4><p>
            Smart classrooms, an upgraded computer lab, and a new library wing
            are added to the campus.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal">
          <span class="year">2025</span><h4>26 Years, 2,400+ Students</h4><p>
            Today the school serves a thriving community of families across
            Ghaziabad with a 98% board result.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="gap:var(--space-xl);">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M2 12s3.5-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3.5 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"
              ></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>
            To be recognised as a leading institution in Ghaziabad that nurtures
            well-rounded individuals — academically strong, ethically grounded,
            and prepared to lead with confidence in a changing world.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle
                cx="12"
                cy="12"
                r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>
            To deliver quality, values-based education through dedicated
            teaching, modern infrastructure, and a safe, supportive environment
            where every student is known, encouraged, and challenged to grow.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">What We Stand For</span>
        <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center">
          <div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10Z"
              ></path></svg>
          </div><h3>Integrity</h3><p>
            Honesty and accountability in everything we teach and do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center">
          <div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path
                d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"
              ></path></svg>
          </div><h3>Respect</h3><p>
            For teachers, peers, elders, and every member of our community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center">
          <div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle><path
                d="M15.5 13.5 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.5-8.5"></path></svg>
          </div><h3>Excellence</h3><p>
            Encouraging every student to do their genuine personal best.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center">
          <div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"
              ></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path
                d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path
                d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>
          </div><h3>Community</h3><p>
            A school that feels like an extended family for every student.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split reverse-mobile">
      <div class="reveal image-frame">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571019613454-1cb2f99b2d8b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Principal addressing students in a school assembly"
          loading="lazy"
          class=""
        />
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Leadership</span>
        <h2>A Message From Our Principal</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          &ldquo;Every child who walks through our gates carries a different
          story and a different strength. Our task as educators is to notice it,
          nurture it, and help it grow into confidence.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <p>
          Mrs. Sunita Sharma has led Saraswati Shiksha Niketan since 2014,
          bringing over two decades of teaching and academic administration
          experience. Under her leadership, the school has strengthened its
          academic outcomes while expanding co-curricular opportunities for
          students at every level.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Governance</span>
        <h2>Management Committee</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          Our school is guided by an experienced management committee committed
          to sustainable, student-first growth.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <h4>Mr. Rajendra Prasad</h4><p class="person-role">
            Chairman, Managing Committee
          </p><p>
            Overseeing institutional strategy and long-term campus development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <h4>Mrs. Kavita Prasad</h4><p class="person-role">
            Vice Chairperson
          </p><p>
            Leading community outreach and parent engagement initiatives.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <h4>Mr. Anil Gupta</h4><p class="person-role">Secretary</p><p>
            Responsible for administrative governance and compliance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <h4>Mrs. Sunita Sharma</h4><p class="person-role">
            Principal &amp; Academic Director
          </p><p>
            Leading day-to-day academic operations and faculty development.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Recognition</span>
        <h2>School Achievements</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="2025">
          <div class="icon-badge">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"></circle><path
                d="M15.5 13.5 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.5-8.5"></path></svg>
          </div><h3>Best Co-Ed School, Vijay Nagar Zone</h3><p>
            Recognised by the Ghaziabad District Education Forum for academic
            performance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="2024">
          <div class="icon-badge">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M8 21h8"></path><path d="M12 17v4"></path><path
                d="M7 4h10v5a5 5 0 0 1-10 0Z"></path><path
                d="M17 5.5h2.5a2 2 0 0 1 0 4H17"></path><path
                d="M7 5.5H4.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4H7"></path></svg>
          </div><h3>State-Level Science Olympiad</h3><p>
            Three students represented Uttar Pradesh at the national science
            talent round.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-ribbon reveal" data-ribbon="2023">
          <div class="icon-badge">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              ><path d="M8 21h8"></path><path d="M12 17v4"></path><path
                d="M7 4h10v5a5 5 0 0 1-10 0Z"></path><path
                d="M17 5.5h2.5a2 2 0 0 1 0 4H17"></path><path
                d="M7 5.5H4.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4H7"></path></svg>
          </div><h3>District Sports Championship</h3><p>
            Under-17 kabaddi and athletics teams brought home district-level
            titles.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="admission-banner reveal">
        <div>
          <h2>Looking Ahead</h2>
          <p class="lede" style="color:#cfd9f2;">
            Our five-year roadmap includes a new digital library wing, expanded
            STEM labs, and a dedicated performing arts auditorium — continuing
            our commitment to holistic, future-ready education.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/admissions" class="btn btn-gold">Join Our Journey</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
